# MVP Priority Gate

- Every coding task must map to a current MVP goal before implementation.
- If work is Phase 2/3 or "nice to have", pause and ask for explicit approval.
- Prefer shipping one complete user flow over starting multiple partial features.
- Prioritize launch-critical flows: auth, onboarding, listings, chat, reliability.
- When trade-offs appear, choose simpler delivery over architectural perfection.
- Keep decisions tied to timeline risk reduction and user impact in Cameroon launch.
